{"000-section": {"000-title": "Punjab Farm Loan Waiver Scheme 3rd Phase \u2013 2.15 Lakh Farmers Debt to be Waived"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "Punjab Farm Loan Waiver Scheme 3rd phase to start to waive off cooperative bank loans of 2.15 lakh small farmers having landholdings between 2.5 to 5 acres, debt waiver scheme 2nd phase (karja mafi scheme) completed in which govt. waived off commercial bank loans of 1.09 lakh marginal farmers with an outlay of Rs. 1771 crore"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Punjab Debt Waiver Scheme Phase 3", "001-normal": "Punjab govt. had started [Farm Loan Waiver Scheme in 2017](https://sarkariyojana.com/punjab-farm-crop-loan-waiver-scheme-2017/) to waive off farm loans upto Rs. 2 lakh of all marginal farmers and also to provide waiver to small farmers who had taken loans upto Rs. 2 lakh under the scheme. In the [1st phase of Debt Waiver Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/punjab-debt-waiver-scheme-crop-loan-waiver-small-farmers/), the state govt. waived off cooperative bank loans of 3.18 lakh marginal farmers of Mansa, Bathinda, Faridkot, Muktsar and Moga districts amounting to a total sum of Rs. 1,815 crore.", "002-normal": "On 7 Dec 2018, govt. has waived Rs. 1,771 crore commercial bank loans of 1.09 lakh marginal farmers in the 2nd phase. The farmers covered in the 2nd phase of debt waiver scheme belong to the districts of Patiala, Ludhiana, Sangrur and Fatehgarh Sahib.", "003-normal": "Now, CM announced the extension of the farm loan waiver scheme to farmers having landholding of 2.5 to 5 acres. These farmers would get debt waiver for loans of cooperative and commercial banks. In the Debt Waiver Scheme 3rd phase, cooperative bank loans of around 2.15 lakh small farmers would be waived off. Moreover in the Farm loan Waiver Scheme 4th phase, commercial bank loans of around 50,752 small farmers would be waived off.", "004-normal": "In the 1st phase of [#KarzaMafi](https://twitter.com/hashtag/KarzaMafi?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw) scheme, my Government had successfully waived off farm loans owed by farmers to cooperative banks & is now waiving off loans owed to commercial banks. I stand committed towards achieving my Govt's goal of 'Karza Kurki Khatam, Fasal Di Puri Rakam'. [pic.twitter.com/zCzBTW08eW](https://t.co/zCzBTW08eW)", "005-normal": "\u2014 Capt.Amarinder Singh (@capt\\_amarinder) [December 6, 2018](https://twitter.com/capt_amarinder/status/1070702593863761920?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)", "006-normal": "  \n **Also Read** \u2013 [MP Farmer Loan Waiver Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/mp-kisan-karz-mafi-yojana-farm-loan-waiver-scheme-farmers/)", "007-normal": "The state govt. of Punjab is also committed to waive off loans of landless labourers in the next phases of the implementation of Karza Mafi scheme."}}